deck: Illustrator, writer, creator of the Ghost Variant group, and former owner of Chapel Hill Comics (2003-2014).
description:
Wander Lane aka Andrew Neal was the owner of Chapel Hill Comics for eleven years until 2014. He is the creator of the Ghost Variant group and designed the following logos that are still in use:

  • Chapel Hill Comics logo
  • Ghost Variant logo
  • Local Comic Shop Day logo
name: Wander Lane
